p: The chemical composition of APNO ( Table 1) showed higher concentrations of saturated fatty acids (28.9% lauric, 12.2% myristic, and 10.7% palmitic acid), followed by monounsaturated (30.7% oleic acid) and polyunsaturated (4.75% linoleic acid). The other fatty acids found in APNO showed concentrations below 4.5%.
